</figure>
</section>

<section>
<title>Spyder</title>
<p>
Spyder - <url href="https://www.spyder-ide.org/">https://www.spyder-ide.org/</url><xref ref="spyder"/> is a powerful IDE that is widely used in the scientific Python community. The figure below is a screenshot of what Spyder looks like with a sine graph plotted. 
</p>
<figure>
<image width="73%" source="Spyder.png" />
<caption>Example Sine Graph in Spyder</caption>
